&lt;p&gt;Filed in &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.nigerianbestforum.com/job/category/thursday-jobs/&quot; rel=&quot;category tag&quot;&gt;Thursday&lt;/a&gt; by &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.nigerianbestforum.com/job/author/cooljoe/&quot; title=&quot;Posts by cooljoe&quot; rel=&quot;author&quot;&gt;cooljoe&lt;/a&gt; on November 10, 2016 • &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.nigerianbestforum.com/job/job-recruitment-at-the-ondo-state-university-of-medical-sciences-thursday-10-november-2016/#respond&quot; rel=&quot;bookmark&quot; title=&quot;Comments for Job Recruitment at the Ondo State University of Medical Sciences, Thursday 10, November 2016&quot;&gt;0 Comments&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ondo State University of Medical Sciences is a top ranking University in Nigeria and indeed the nation’s pride. Established in 2015, the university has grown tremendously, stretching its academic disciplines and research across six different schools and over thirty academic departments.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Applications are hereby invited from suitably qualified candidates to fill the following academic positions below:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ASSISTANT LECTURER&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DEPARTMENTS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Computer Science&lt;br/&gt;Biology&lt;br/&gt;Physics&lt;br/&gt;Chemistry&lt;br/&gt;Medical Rehabilitation&lt;br/&gt;Nursing&lt;br/&gt;Mathematics&lt;br/&gt;Physiotherapy&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;QUALIFICATIONS AND REQUIREMENTS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Candidates must have at least a Second Class (Upper Division) Honours Degree and in addition, a Masters degree in relevant discipline&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PROFESSOR&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DEPARTMENTS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Computer Science&lt;br/&gt;Biology&lt;br/&gt;Physics&lt;br/&gt;Chemistry&lt;br/&gt;Medical Rehabilitation&lt;br/&gt;Nursing&lt;br/&gt;Mathematics&lt;br/&gt;Physiotherapy&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;QUALIFICATIONS AND REQUIREMENTS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Candidates must have not less than ten (10) years of teaching and Research experience in a University.&lt;br/&gt;He/She must possess Doctorate degree in the Sciences.&lt;br/&gt;The possession of requisite basic degrees that are registerable by different professional bodies is required for those applying to this Faculty and Department.&lt;br/&gt;The ability to initiate and direct research projects, the possession of reasonable administrative experience and substantial scholarly publications in reputable journals are important considerations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;LECTURER II&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DEPARTMENTS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Computer Science&lt;br/&gt;Biology&lt;br/&gt;Physics&lt;br/&gt;Chemistry&lt;br/&gt;Medical Rehabilitation&lt;br/&gt;Nursing&lt;br/&gt;Mathematics&lt;br/&gt;Physiotherapy&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;QUALIFICATIONS AND REQUIREMENTS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Candidates must have at least MBBS or BchD&lt;br/&gt;He/She must possess a Fellowship degree in Medicine/Medical Science Course.&lt;br/&gt;The possession of requisite basic degrees that are registerable by different professional bodies is required for those applying to this Faculty and Department.&lt;br/&gt;He/ She must have at least three (3) years experience in teaching and Research in a University or an equivalent institution, with some Published articles in reputable Journals.&lt;br/&gt;They must show proof of additional scholarship and willingness to participate in research in the Department they are applying to.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;LECTURER I&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DEPARTMENTS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Computer Science&lt;br/&gt;Biology&lt;br/&gt;Physics&lt;br/&gt;Chemistry&lt;br/&gt;Medical Rehabilitation&lt;br/&gt;Nursing&lt;br/&gt;Mathematics&lt;br/&gt;Physiotherapy&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;QUALIFICATIONS AND REQUIREMENTS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Candidates must have at least MBBS or BchD&lt;br/&gt;He/She must possess a Fellowship degree in Medicine/Medical Science Course.&lt;br/&gt;The possession of requisite basic degrees that are registerable by different professional bodies is required for those applying to this Faculty and Department.&lt;br/&gt;He/ She must have at least three (3) years experience in teaching and Research in a University or an equivalent institution, with some Published articles in reputable Journals.&lt;br/&gt;They must show proof of additional scholarship and willingness to participate in research in the Department they are applying to.&lt;br/&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br/&gt;READER&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DEPARTMENTS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Computer Science&lt;br/&gt;Biology&lt;br/&gt;Physics&lt;br/&gt;Chemistry&lt;br/&gt;Medical Rehabilitation&lt;br/&gt;Nursing&lt;br/&gt;Mathematics&lt;br/&gt;Physiotherapy&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;QUALIFICATIONS AND REQUIREMENTS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Candidates must have not less than ten (10) years of teaching and Research experience in a University.&lt;br/&gt;He/She must possess a Fellowship degree in Medicine/Medical Science Course.&lt;br/&gt;The possession of requisite basic degrees that are registerable by different professional bodies is required for those applying to this Faculty and Department.&lt;br/&gt;The ability to initiate and direct research projects, the possession of reasonable administrative experience and substantial scholarly publications in reputable journals are important considerations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SENIOR LECTURER&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DEPARTMENTS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Computer Science&lt;br/&gt;Biology&lt;br/&gt;Physics&lt;br/&gt;Chemistry&lt;br/&gt;Medical Rehabilitation&lt;br/&gt;Nursing&lt;br/&gt;Mathematics&lt;br/&gt;Physiotherapy&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;QUALIFICATIONS AND REQUIREMENTS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Candidates must have at least (6) years of teaching and Research experience in a University.&lt;br/&gt;He/She must possess Doctorate degree in the Sciences.&lt;br/&gt;The possession of requisite basic degrees that are registerable by different professional bodies is required for those applying to this Faculty and Department.&lt;br/&gt;The candidates must have substantial publications in reputable journals, and have the ability to initiate research and to mentor junior staff and students.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;TO APPLY&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Applicants should send 10 copies of their applications with detailed curriculum vitae (that includes educational qualifications and relevant experience) to:&lt;br/&gt;The Registrar,&lt;br/&gt;Ondo State University of Medical Science,&lt;br/&gt;Laje Road, Ondo,&lt;br/&gt;Ondo State.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DUE DATE:&lt;/strong&gt; 18 November, 2016&lt;/p&gt;
