&lt;p&gt;An international Boarding School located in Lagos State is currently seeking applications from qualified and experienced individual to fill the position below:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIAL EDUCATION NEEDS COORDINATOR AND ASSISTANT&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;REQUIREMENTS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Candidate should possess relevant qualification.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FACILITIES SUPERVISOR&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;REQUIREMENTS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Candidate should possess relevant qualification&lt;br/&gt;Candidates must have an experienced in managing cleaning teams, gardeners and estate management&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CATERING MANAGER&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;JOB DESCRIPTION&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br/&gt;To head the school cafeteria and kitchen&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;REQUIREMENTS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Must have a passion for food.&lt;br/&gt;Must have experience of running a professional kitchen and cafeteria&lt;br/&gt;Must have a background in Food and Nutrition Science&lt;br/&gt;Must have a background in Food and Nutrition Sciences.&lt;br/&gt;Should possess a qualification in Hotel Management and Food Safety.&lt;br/&gt;Excellent cooking skills.&lt;br/&gt;Plan menus based on Nutritional requirements for growing children.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;TO APPLY&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Applicants should send their applications, CV’s and passport picture to: &lt;a class=&quot;bbc_email&quot; href=&quot;mailto:internationalschjobs@gmail.com&quot;&gt;internationalschjobs@gmail.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Note&lt;br/&gt;Only experienced and qualified candidates with school experience are required to apply for the position. More details will be shared at the interview.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Only shortlisted candidates will be invited for interview.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DUE DATE:&lt;/strong&gt; 22 November, 2016&lt;/p&gt;
