&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Vaastrop Nigeria Limited&lt;/strong&gt; was first founded in 1989 as Pace Engineering Services with offices in Enugu, Katsina and Kano. It went through different developmental stages over several years and finally became incorporated as Vaastrop Nigeria Limited in April 1997.&lt;/p&gt;
