&lt;li&gt;English Language, Economics and Mathematics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;em&gt;Relevant Credits:&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Commerce, Government, Civic Education, Accounting, Geography and History&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Course: BA French&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;General Requirement:&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;5 credit passes in not more than 2 sittings including English Language and Mathematics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;English Language, Economics and Mathematics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;em&gt;Relevant Credits:&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Economics, Geography, Government, Civic Education and History&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Course: BSc Geography&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;General Requirement:&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;5 credit passes in not more than 2 sittings including English Language and Mathematics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;English Language, Economics and Mathematics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;em&gt;Relevant Credits&lt;/em&gt;:&lt;br/&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;History, Economics, Government, Civic Education Physics, Chemistry and Biology (preference will be given to those having credits in social science subjects).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Course: BA History&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;General Requirement:&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;5 credit passes in not more than 2 sittings including English Language and Mathematics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;English Language, History or Government/Civil Education and Mathematics&lt;/li&gt;
